Race.Name: Human
Race.Description: Humans are the baseline race against which all other races are measured. They are average in most respects but get a bonus feat and bonus skill points when they level up.

Race.Name: Dwarf
Race.Description: Dwarves are a hardy race of warriors and craftsmen renowned for the weapons and armor they create and their stonecrafting skills.

Race.Name: Elf
Race.Description: Elves are a race of long lived humanoids that look like humans but are slender with pointed ears. They are at home with nature and are renowned for their skill with bows and with magic.

Race.Name: Hobbit
Race.Description: Hobbits are a shy race that look similar to humans but are shorter with hairy feet and large bellies. They are adept at not being noticed by larger folk.

Race.Name: Gnome
Race.Description: Gnomes are a short humanoid known for their skill with artifacts and their propensity to practice prankery.

Race.Name: Dark Elf
Race.Description: Dark elves or drow are dark skinned elves that live underground and are adapted to living under those conditions.

Race.Name: Orc
Race.Description: Orcs are a beastial race known for their violent natures and skill in combat.

Race.Name: Minotaur
Race.Description: Minotaurs are a large beastial race of skilled warriors who regularly test themselves in gladatorial combat.

Race.Name: Ogre
Race.Description: Ogres are a large brutish race. Their large size and strength make them natural, if dimwitted, warriors.

Race.Name: Fe-lion
Race.Description: Fe-lions are a race of dextrous, acrobatic catmen.

Race.Name: Rattus
Race.Description: Rattus are a race of devious and quick ratmen known for slinking in shadows. Many of them tend towards more nefarious professions.

Race.Name: Werewolf
Race.Description: Werewolves are a race of cursed wolfmen. They are strong and fast and skilled with their claws but are weak towards silver weapons.

Race.Name: Draconian
Race.Description: Draconians are a race of noble dragon-men known for their agility and skill with magic.

Race.Name: Lizardman
Race.Description: Lizardman are a tough, brutish race not known for their intelligence. They make very powerful warriors if properly motivated.

Race.Name: Seraphim
Race.Description: Seraphim are a race of winged angelic beings from the heavens, they are the least powerful form of angels. They are known for possessing the wisdom beyond mortal races.

Race.Name: Cambion
Race.Description: Cambions are the spawn of fallen angels and humans. Clever and devious, few trust them due to their infernal parentage.

Race.Name: Ignis
Race.Description: Ignis are a race of outsiders from the planes of fire. They tend to be both quick and quick-tempered.

Race.Name: Hydros
Race.Description: Hydros are a race of outsiders from the planes of water. They tend to be patient and wise.

Race.Name: Granote
Race.Description: Granote are a race of outsiders from the planes of earth and stone. They are slower to act but very tough.

Race.Name: Aetheri
Race.Description: Aetheri are a race of outsiders from the planes of air. They are quick and tend to talk very fast.

Race.Name: Lich
Race.Description: Lich are undead former humanoids who have achieved a type of immortality by trapping their souls into an object. They are usually magic users of some sort.

Race.Name: Wampyri
Race.Description: Wampyri are undead former humanoids who have been cursed with vampirism either by their wills or against it.

Race.Name: Goblin
Race.Description: Goblins are a small, weak subspecies of orcs.

Race.Name: Uruk-Hai
Race.Description: Uruk-hai are a subspecies of orcs mutated and bred by dark sorcerers.
